Block Elements:
Starts from new line 
Take up all horizontal space.
can have margins and paddings
width and height can be set
examples: <div>,<p>,<h1>,<ul>,<li>

Inline Elements:
Stay in the line with text 
just as wide as content 
no new line between Elements
can't set size easily
examples: <span>,<a>,<strong>,<em>,<img>